summary: An ordinance zoning and establishing Use, Area and Height Districts on portions of Sections 1, 2 and 3 in Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W. M. and on portions of Sections 27, 28, 29, 33, 34 and 35 in Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W. M., annexed to the City of Seattle under Ordinances No. 81655 and No. 81704 on March 1, 1953, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, to embrace such area.
